198
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,300
Eu darei.

199
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,070
Yuri!

200
00:15:00,070 --> 00:15:02,820
Essa é nossa criança.

201
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:04,830
Eu dar a luz e criá-lo.

202
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:06,600
